        <h1>We Care Daily Clinics</h1>

        <p>Medical tenant improvements demand specialized knowledge of healthcare regulations, infection control requirements, and the unique operational needs of clinical environments. The We Care Daily Clinics project in Seattle showcases our expertise in transforming standard commercial space into fully functional, code-compliant medical facilities.</p>

        <p>Healthcare construction operates under stringent regulatory requirements that go far beyond typical commercial builds. We navigated complex building codes specific to medical use, implemented specialized HVAC systems for infection control and patient comfort, created examination rooms meeting clinical standards and ADA requirements, installed medical-grade lighting and power systems, and coordinated specialized plumbing for clinical sinks and medical equipment.</p>

        <p>Beyond technical compliance, we designed spaces that support efficient clinical workflows while maintaining a welcoming environment for patients. The layout balances privacy for patient care with staff efficiency, incorporates proper waiting areas and administrative functions, and uses finishes that meet healthcare cleanliness standards while creating a comfortable, professional atmosphere.</p>

        <h3>Project Highlights</h3>
        <ul style="line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <li>Medical tenant improvement meeting healthcare building codes</li>
          <li>Multiple examination rooms with clinical infrastructure</li>
          <li>Specialized HVAC systems for infection control and patient comfort</li>
          <li>Medical-grade electrical and lighting systems</li>
          <li>ADA-compliant design throughout patient and staff areas</li>
          <li>Layout supporting efficient clinical workflows</li>
          <li>Professional finishes meeting healthcare cleanliness standards</li>
          <li>Coordination with building management in occupied commercial building</li>
        </ul>

        <p>The We Care Daily Clinics project demonstrates Northway's versatility across commercial sectors and our ability to handle specialized tenant improvements with complex regulatory requirements. Whether it's medical facilities, professional offices, or retail spaces, we bring the expertise needed to transform commercial space into functional, compliant environments that serve their intended purpose.</p>
